&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;AgWest Farm Credit is a member-owned financial cooperative that provides financing and related services to farmers, ranchers, agribusinesses, commercial fishermen, timber producers, rural homeowners and crop insurance customers in a seven-state territory in the Western United States. AgWest is part of the 100+ year-old Farm Credit System – the leading provider of credit to American agriculture.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;AgWest champions the growth and advancement of agriculture, the value of rural communities, and the vital contribution our customers make to the economy and society. We serve customers in 59 locations throughout the West.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;We are in search of a Corporate Administrative Specialist I or Corporate Administrative Specialist II to join our Corporate Administration department in Rocklin, California. This full-time position reports to the Manager, Corporate Administration and will manage front desk operations, streamline office supplies and snacks for regional offices, handle shipping logistics, and procure IT hardware. This role ensures smooth daily operations and a welcoming environment for visitors and employees across our corporate locations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compensation Information&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The base salary range for this position in Rocklin, California is:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Level I:&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;Typical starting range: $46,200 - $59,500&lt;br&gt;Full base salary range: $46,200 - $66,200&lt;br&gt;Annual performance-based incentive target is 6% of base.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Level II:&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;Typical starting range: $50,400 - $67,300&lt;br&gt;Full base salary range: $50,400 - $75,700&lt;br&gt;Annual performance-based incentive target is 6% of base.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;*Relocation assistance will be provided to eligible candidates who must relocate to accept this position.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Essential Duties&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Front Desk &amp;amp; Reception
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage the Rocklin reception desk by providing exceptional, welcoming service to visitors and vendors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Answer the main phone line and route inquiries efficiently to the appropriate departments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Process daily incoming and outgoing mail.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Receive, log, and manage FedEx, UPS, and Amazon deliveries daily.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Office Management &amp;amp; Procurement
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Process and monitor snack orders and office supplies for the Rocklin and broader assigned regions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Approve and manage office supply purchasing orders for assigned region offices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Order, track, and inventory standard IT hardware (headsets, keyboards, mice, webcams) for new hire setups and employee replacement requests.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Logistics &amp;amp; Employee Recognition
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage all FedEx packing and shipping requests for corporate staff.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Process and coordinate the distribution of monthly service awards across assigned region.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform all duties and maintain all standards in accordance with company policies, procedures, and internal controls.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Other duties as assigned.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Travel Requirements&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;AgWest employees may occasionally be asked to travel for all-staff or team meetings not included in the standard travel requirements for the role.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
